A vegan diet is plant-based and one which doesn’t include any products that
are derived from animals - dairy, meat, and other by-products such as honey.
Veganism is fast becoming an increasingly popular lifestyle and dietary choice
for many people and there are now scores of dedicated vegan restaurants,
vegan-friendly ingredients in supermarkets, and vegan cookbooks readily
